  "texts": [
    "Therefore, it's essential for educators to model exemplary behavior (Hirsh-Pasek & Blinkoff 2023).",
    "As we have reviewed, the impact of LLM like ChatGPT in education is enormous.",
    "Another field that has been heavily affected by the extensive large language processing models includes healthcare system.",
    "It was shown that 60% of doctor visits are for minor diseases, and 80% of them can be treated at home by using simple remedies (Bhirud et al. 2019, Frangoudes et al. 2021, Cascella et al. 2023).",
    "These diseases usually include cold, cough, headache, abdominal pains and so on."
  ]
